transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Ha sir jo aapne photo bheja na,
Customer: Ek lead aagyi abhi pehle wo consume kar lijiye fir mai bata deta hu aapko.
Customer: Kya?
Executive: Accha wo edit kiye hai. Sir lead to aa rahi hai matlab time hoti hai na to wo thoda time jyada deti hai interest matlab jo timing hai na wo matching matching nahi ho pa rahi hai aap logo ki isliye. Kya ho gaya? Leads aa rahi hai sir matlab leads proper aa rahi hai dikkat pata hai kya aa rahi hai ho sakta hai ki sir aap matlab proper time nahi de pa rahe ho sir. Kyu?
Customer: IndiaMART ko. Sir abhi dekhiye ha ha ha ha bataiye. 24 over october mobile teeno tino divas mere hath me hai aur mai teeno ko khol ke baitha hu akela aur mai chutti par hu abhi duty pe nahi hu mai abhi. Accha accha. Chutti nahi maine 15-20 din ki madam chutti nahi to maine chutti le rakhi hai apne kaam ke liye alag se. Koi aur reason andar aaya hai kya hum dekh rahe hai. Hmm hmm hmm hmm. Sir lead mai to bolta nahi aapko subah se mai isliye to bol raha hu aapne call nahi kiya 25 minutes ho 200 bar notify 100-200 bar notify kiya hai aaj ko tab bhi kuch nahi aa raha uske andar. Subah jaise maine dekhne laga 500 ke liye ki wo out. Jaise dekhne laga within second ke andar aap kahiye matlab notification nahi aaya mai khol ke baitha hua hu aate hi liya aur wo gaya waha se. To subah se kitne lead aapne consume kari hai sir?
Customer: Wo dekho na aap uske andar. Uh kitni lead kya consume kari hai aaj?
Executive: Lead ka change ye apna dwara 46 kiya hai. Fir aapne ye aaj ka kiya tha ye. Kal ka hai sir ji kal ka aaj ka kuch nahi hai.
Customer: Ek minute sir.
Executive: Accha kal aapne itni sari kar li sir hai na aaj aaj hi dikkat aayi hai aapko.
Customer: Mai kyuki mai leke baitha hu na isko sath me akela baitha hu do din se mai to chutti par mai chutti le li maine special me kaam ke liye. Thoda sa dekh lo sir kyuki mere ko na timing ka issue lag raha hai mujhe jaha tak lag raha hai kyuki mere end se to koi dikkat nahi hai fir bhi mai ek bar check kar leta hu sir agar kuch problem hai to. Nahi matlab ye nahi hai timing kaise issue ho sakta hai mai susu nahi karne ja raha hu batao abhi second me to. Khana nahi khaya subah se aapne second me to baithe baithe. Sir khana khana kha lo aaram se aap lunch kare to aapne lunch kiya na maine lunch bhi nahi kiya abhi tak. Nahi nahi sir. Is second me ki sir kuch aa jaye kuch aa jaye kuch aa jaye. Ye baat mujhko nahi bol sakta ki mai yaha pe online nahi hu mai aapko online dikha dunga practically proof karke ki mai kab se is pe leke baitha hu is leke isko. Dekhiye kal kal kal to aapne achi khasi lead consume kari hai sir hai na par aaj dikkat hui hai. Kal to aapne achi khasi lead usse pehle bhi aapne achi khasi kiye hue hai. Matlab regular basis par theek hi ho raha hai sir kahi koi dikkat nahi aayi hai aaj hi dikkat aayi hai. Chalo sir mere ko 4 baje tak ka time do. Thik hai? Hmm. Aadha ghanta do thik hai aur baki ek bar thoda sa timing ka thoda dhyan rakhna aur lunch kar lo sir aap thik hai. Aur aapne timing to mai leke baitha hu usko pure. 9696 pe aapne bhej diya wo jo aapne bheja na photo mere number pe hi bheja tha sir. Matlab direct mere pe hi aayega. Isko bhej diya are waha par naam wo save tha wo Sonu naam se. Nahi nahi wo wo wo dekha to kuch aur hi reply aa raha hai. Wo delete kar diya mujhe pata hai ki waha pe wo alag tha scene mujhe pata hai in sab cheez ka fir maine waha pe bhi are ye to galat maine kaha ye to apne aap kaise aa sakta hai ye to company wo system se aa raha hai message aa raha hai ye to. Ha ha ye mera personal number hai sir jispe matlab ki jo hai aapke whatsapp pe. Jis jis jis se aapne mere ko voice call kiya hai na wo mera personal number hai wo. Thik hai ek bar dekhna zara suno abhi dekho isko yaar kyuki bina leads ke to fir kaam chalega nahi isko. Thik hai aur inquiry bhi dekh lenge ek bar sir filter karke ek bar thik hai. Inquiry me filter karke dekh raha hu bar bar dekh raha hu filter kar raha hu aa hi nahi rahi usme kya to waha blank pada hai sab kuch. Thik hai sir aap mere ko time dijiye thik hai mai aapko call back karunga isko mai close kar raha hu jo aapne bheja tha 9696. Thik hai sir? Okay.
